---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { withBase } from "../lib/paths";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="祝庆 Zhu Qing | 影视后期与 Unreal Engine 开发"
    description="祝庆的个人作品集首页，聚焦影视后期、UE5、虚拟制片、MetaHuman 与视觉设计。"
    activePath="/"
>
    <main class="home-hero">
        <div class="home-grid">
            <section class="profile-col" data-reveal>
                <div class="cinematic-frame">
                    <img src={withBase("/images/home/zq.jpg")} alt="祝庆 Zhu Qing cinematic portfolio still" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
                </div>

                <p class="eyebrow">Film Technology / UE Development</p>
                <h1>祝庆 Zhu Qing</h1>
                <div class="role-tags" aria-label="Profile tags">
                    <span>BFA Student</span>
                    <span class="divider"></span>
                    <span>MetaHuman</span>
                    <span class="divider"></span>
                    <span>Post-Production</span>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="bio-col" data-reveal>
                <div class="language-tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="Language">
                    <button class="active" type="button" data-lang-button="cn" aria-controls="content-cn">中文</button>
                    <button type="button" data-lang-button="en" aria-controls="content-en">EN</button>
                </div>

                <div id="content-cn" class="lang-content active" data-lang-panel="cn">
                    <p class="lead">
                        我是北京电影学院影视技术方向学生，关注<strong>影视后期</strong>、<strong>虚幻引擎开发</strong>与<strong>视觉设计</strong>之间的交叉表达。
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        我使用 UE5 复刻过《底特律：化身为人》的章节级交互，熟悉 nDisplay 虚拟制片背景墙流程，也持续研究 MetaHuman 与数字人光场采集工作流。
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        在剪辑与调色方向，我参与过短片和商业项目后期，并与小红书、Disney、国家地理等品牌有过合作。目前正在探索 3D 立体拍摄、实时影像与调色流程的结合。
                    </p>
                    <div class="contact-box">
                        <span>如果你对研究项目、电影制作、技术开发，或者只是单纯想聊聊历史与影像如何结合，欢迎通过邮件与我联系。</span>
                        <a href="mailto:zq_eugene@qq.com">zq_eugene@qq.com</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="content-en" class="lang-content" data-lang-panel="en" hidden>
                    <p class="lead">
                        I am a Film & TV Technology student at Beijing Film Academy, working across <strong>post-production</strong>, <strong>Unreal Engine</strong>, and <strong>visual design</strong>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        I have recreated interactive chapters from <em>Detroit: Become Human</em> in UE5, with hands-on experience in nDisplay virtual production workflows and MetaHuman research.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        As an editor and color-focused maker, I have worked on short films and commercial projects for brands including Xiaohongshu, Disney, and National Geographic.
                    </p>
                    <div class="contact-box">
                        <span>Technical dev, filmmaking, or visual collaboration</span>
                        <a href="mailto:zq_eugene@qq.com">zq_eugene@qq.com</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script>
        const buttons = document.querySelectorAll("[data-lang-button]");
        const panels = document.querySelectorAll("[data-lang-panel]");

        buttons.forEach((button) => {
            button.addEventListener("click", () => {
                const lang = button.getAttribute("data-lang-button");

                buttons.forEach((item) => item.classList.toggle("active", item === button));
                panels.forEach((panel) => {
                    const active = panel.getAttribute("data-lang-panel") === lang;
                    panel.classList.toggle("active", active);
                    panel.toggleAttribute("hidden", !active);
                });
            });
        });
    </script>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .home-hero {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding: calc(var(--header-height) + 56px) var(--page-x) 64px;
    }

    .home-grid {
        width: min(100%, 1280px);
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(320px, 1.12fr);
        gap: clamp(42px, 8vw, 104px);
        align-items: center;
    }

    .profile-col h1 {
        margin: 10px 0 18px;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: clamp(2.35rem, 13cqw, 5.4rem);
        line-height: 0.92;
        letter-spacing: 0;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .profile-col {
        container-type: inline-size;
    }

    @supports not (font-size: 1cqw) {
        .profile-col h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.35rem, 5.2vw, 5.4rem);
        }
    }

    .cinematic-frame {
        width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 2.35 / 1;
        margin-bottom: 34px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 4px;
        background: #111;
        box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.52);
    }

    .cinematic-frame img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        filter: saturate(0.82) contrast(1.12) brightness(0.78);
        transition: transform 8s ease, filter 600ms ease;
    }

    .cinematic-frame:hover img {
        transform: scale(1.045);
        filter: saturate(0.9) contrast(1.16) brightness(0.9);
    }

    .role-tags {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
        font-size: 0.83rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .divider {
        width: 4px;
        height: 4px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: currentColor;
        opacity: 0.5;
    }

    .bio-col {
        min-height: 420px;
    }

    .language-tabs {
        display: inline-flex;
        gap: 4px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        padding: 4px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
    }

    .language-tabs button {
        min-width: 58px;
        border: 0;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        cursor: pointer;
        font: inherit;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        padding: 7px 14px;
        transition: background 180ms ease, color 180ms ease;
    }

    .language-tabs button:hover,
    .language-tabs button.active {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.11);
        color: #fff;
    }

    .lang-content {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(10px);
        transition: opacity 260ms ease, transform 260ms ease;
    }

    .lang-content.active {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .lang-content p {
        margin: 0 0 1.35rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.45vw, 1.12rem);
        line-height: 1.86;
    }

    .lang-content .lead {
        color: var(--text-main);
        font-size: clamp(1.14rem, 2vw, 1.42rem);
        font-weight: 520;
    }

    .lang-content strong {
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 650;
    }

    .contact-box {
        display: grid;
        gap: 8px;
        margin-top: 44px;
        padding-top: 28px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .contact-box span {
        color: var(--text-dim);
        font-size: 0.86rem;
    }

    .contact-box a {
        width: fit-content;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 180ms ease;
    }

    .contact-box a:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .home-hero {
            align-items: flex-start;
            padding-top: calc(var(--header-height) + 44px);
        }

        .home-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 42px;
        }

        .cinematic-frame {
            aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
        }

        .bio-col {
            min-height: 0;
        }
    }
</style>
